Author: scifichick774 <br>
Rating: PG-13 <br>
Category: Drama/Humor (kind of like the show), K/N Angst/UST <br>
Spoilers: Don't think there are any specific references to any eppies, but just to be safe; anything through the end of the show (sob) is fair game. <br>
Summary: Kate meets a seemingly perfect guy around St. Patrick's Day and the unit gets assigned to a case regarding a leprechaun. <br>
